--- 10.3  Realtime Live Count ---
[ ] Subscribe to scan_logs INSERT events via Supabase Realtime
[ ] Update attendance counter in real-time without page refresh
[ ] Show "X people checked in" live counter on scan page for scanner staff
[ ] WHY: Realtime via Supabase uses Postgres logical replication — no polling

--- 10.4  Scan History / Audit Log ---
[ ] Paginated table: ticket token (truncated), attendee, result, scanner, time, IP
[ ] Filter by: session, date range, result type, scanner
[ ] Export to CSV

--- 10.5  Analytics Components ---
